===Transitive verb===
'''to housebreak''' ([[housebroken]])

To [[train]] an [[animal]] to [[avoid]] [[urinate|urinating]] or [[defecate|defecating]] in the [[house]], except within a [[litterbox]], [[toilet]], or other [[receptacle]].

